I would like to mention that in
addition to Sundeck's work

108
00:06:04,322 --> 00:06:06,335
there are a number of
tools and tool boxes

109
00:06:06,490 --> 00:06:08,952
under development to
help you in the collection

110
00:06:09,113 --> 00:06:12,788
analysis, and visualization
of your data.

111
00:06:13,007 --> 00:06:15,757
You may have heard
about the FSM toolbox

112
00:06:15,918 --> 00:06:19,430
the world bank's diagnostic
