the main results of the assessment
of the initial situation and provide

132
00:07:22,996 --> 00:07:26,383
a good advocacy tool
to talk to authorities.

133
00:07:27,087 --> 00:07:30,175
The SFD website is there to
help you make your own SFD

134
00:07:30,323 --> 00:07:33,548
and you can learn more about it
by watching the dedicated module 

135
