actually depends on the quality 

139
00:07:44,261 --> 00:07:46,574
of the assessment of
the initial situation

140
00:07:46,736 --> 00:07:49,673
and how it is communicated.

141
00:07:49,843 --> 00:07:52,905
Don't forget the importance of
the human dimension of

142
00:07:53,074 --> 00:07:54,749
this assessment.

143
00:07:54,917 --> 00:07:58,617
It is the time for first contact
but also the trust building

144
